    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but the exterior has noticeable scratches and a few small dents, while the interior upholstery shows significant wear and staining. It is currently roadworthy, but the buyer should expect to replace the tires soon and address a slow oil leak. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind performing some cosmetic and mechanical touch-ups.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
